      <title>瑞波币规则提振市场情绪，加密货币再次小幅上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/cryptocurrencies-inch-upwards-again-as-ripple-xrp-ruling-lifts-mood</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在 Ripple Labs Inc. 被勒令支付 1.25 亿美元罚款之后，主要加密货币周四小幅上涨，该公司将此结果描述为对美国证券交易委员会的胜利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/cryptocurrencies-inch-upwards-again-as-ripple-xrp-ruling-lifts-mood</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 03:07:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国国有银行在牛市中加大债券销售力度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/china-seven-year-yield-rises-most-since-april-amid-pushback-bets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[交易员表示，中国大型国有银行周四上午大规模出售七年期国债，这一迹象表明当局抑制创纪录债务上涨的举措正在升级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-08/china-seven-year-yield-rises-most-since-april-amid-pushback-bets</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 08 Aug 2024 02:30:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
